555
00:44:33,203 --> 00:44:34,705
But I'm not going to keep a book.

556
00:44:34,772 --> 00:44:36,473
I'm going to memorize everything
in my head.

557
00:44:37,541 --> 00:44:39,009
Later on when I become famous,

558
00:44:39,076 --> 00:44:40,878
