645
00:54:54,491 --> 00:54:55,659
Should I ask him?

646
00:55:04,434 --> 00:55:05,602
I'm so nervous.

647
00:55:08,438 --> 00:55:09,606
But why am I nervous?

648
00:55:11,074 --> 00:55:12,575
I don't know. Whatever.

649
00:56:13,870 --> 00:56:15,405
DILIGENT KID

650
